why we called you here?

292
00:12:50,440 --> 00:12:51,240
I don't know.

293
00:12:51,600 --> 00:12:53,600
I'm just an honest worker.

294
00:12:53,640 --> 00:12:54,880
Still not honest?

295
00:12:55,400 --> 00:12:57,560
You think we don't know your background?

296
00:13:03,600 --> 00:13:04,880
You're from the Association.

297
00:13:05,680 --> 00:13:07,320
Maybe it's Eagle.

298
00:13:07,960 --> 00:13:08,880
or a pole.

299
00:13:09,920 --> 00:13:11,880
Your fingers are long and your limbs are healthy.

300
00:13:13,720 --> 00:13:15,680
So it's a lie that you beg for a meal.

301
00:13:16,560 --> 00:13:17,760
It seems to be the Rong family.

302
00:13:18,360 --> 00:13:19,320
Your Leader

303
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:21,120
Hong Niu, right?

304
00:13:22,480 --> 00:13:23,080
Detective.

305
00:13:24,320 --> 00:13:26,360
Since you know I'm from the Association,

306
00:13:27,000 --> 00:13:29,040
you should know our rules.

307
00:13:30,840 --> 00:13:33,680
The Liuhe Association is always at risk.

308
00:13:34,280 --> 00:13:36,480
Traitors are living in hell.

309
00:13:37,120 --> 00:13:39,080
I’m not asking you to betray the Association.

310
00:13:40,440 --> 00:13:42,560
I just want to know

311
00:13:42,720 --> 00:13:44,600
has anything to do with your Association.

312
00:13:46,600 --> 00:13:48,600
The officer wants to get something from me.

313
00:13:51,200 --> 00:13:51,840
Look.

314
00:13:52,360 --> 00:13:54,320
I won’t interfere

315
00:13:54,640 --> 00:13:55,440
I won't interfere.

316
00:13:56,160 --> 00:13:57,680
But you have to give me

317
00:13:58,000 --> 00:13:58,960
to hand over the case

318
00:13:58,960 --> 00:14:00,360
and close the case, right?

319
00:14:01,720 --> 00:14:02,720
If I can't solve the case,

320
00:14:03,560 --> 00:14:05,400
I can only investigate it.

321
00:14:06,120 --> 00:14:06,960
What's the benefit

322
00:14:07,120 --> 00:14:08,680
will it do to the Association?

323
00:14:09,960 --> 00:14:10,560
Besides,

324
00:14:11,000 --> 00:14:12,240
if you cooperate with the investigation,

325
00:14:12,920 --> 00:14:14,360
I don't think it's betrayal.

326
00:14:22,800 --> 00:14:23,560
Look.

327
00:14:24,360 --> 00:14:25,160
Where's HongNiu?

328
00:14:25,720 --> 00:14:28,600
He's the leader of the Association.

329
00:14:29,360 --> 00:14:30,520
You're nothing.

330
00:14:31,560 --> 00:14:34,040
You said you were locked up in an accident.

331
00:14:34,520 --> 00:14:35,440
They can save you.

332
00:14:36,200 --> 00:14:38,000
Maybe in the end,

333
00:14:40,200 --> 00:14:41,520
to silence him.

334
00:14:45,320 --> 00:14:45,800
How about this?

335
00:14:46,520 --> 00:14:47,360
I'll take another step back.

336
00:14:48,440 --> 00:14:49,560
Say whatever you know.

337
00:14:49,960 --> 00:14:50,720
I'm done.

338
00:14:51,160 --> 00:14:51,680
I'll let you go.

339
00:14:52,280 --> 00:14:52,840
How is it?

340
00:15:00,920 --> 00:15:02,240
I just opened the door

341
00:15:02,720 --> 00:15:03,640
I just opened the door.

342
00:15:04,240 --> 00:15:04,920
Go on.

343
00:15:13,160 --> 00:15:13,600
How is it?

344
00:15:13,960 --> 00:15:14,760
Did you find anything?

345
00:15:15,440 --> 00:15:16,360
Ping

346
00:15:16,840 --> 00:15:19,000
is a member of the Association.

347
00:15:19,880 --> 00:15:22,320
He opened the door

348
00:15:22,600 --> 00:15:24,400
at the wedding.

349
00:15:31,600 --> 00:15:32,880
Does he know who the murderer is?

350
00:15:34,160 --> 00:15:37,840
One is Wu Qi.

351
00:15:38,720 --> 00:15:41,160
and another gentleman.

352
00:15:41,280 --> 00:15:42,040
He doesn’t know him.

353
00:15:43,280 --> 00:15:44,280
Can you ask Wei Qing

354
00:15:44,400 --> 00:15:45,720
help draw the portrait of the suspect?

355
00:15:45,800 --> 00:15:46,840
Fine.

356
00:15:46,920 --> 00:15:47,480
Stop.

357
00:15:49,040 --> 00:15:49,960
Captain said

358
00:15:50,440 --> 00:15:52,240
to stop you from investigating the murder,

359
00:15:52,520 --> 00:15:54,480
Especially the Association.

360
00:15:54,600 --> 00:15:56,280
It's the Chief's taboo.

361
00:15:56,920 --> 00:15:58,240
This won't do either.

362
00:15:58,720 --> 00:15:59,560
Just fire me.

363
00:16:00,360 --> 00:16:01,320
Not really.

364
00:16:01,800 --> 00:16:03,640
You can provide us with clues.

365
00:16:12,200 --> 00:16:14,120
Tell me immediately if there is any new progress.

366
00:16:14,640 --> 00:16:15,160
Yes.

367
00:16:16,160 --> 00:16:16,920
That's more like it.
